<article class="text">
	<header>
		<h1>Barras de Progresso</h1>
		<h3>Usadas para indicar um progresso de carregamento ou ação de envio e etc.</h3>
	</header>

	<div class="example">
		<div class="progress">
		  <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 80%;">
		    <span class="sr-only">80% Completo</span>
		  </div>
		</div>
		<div class="progress">
		  <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 80%;">
		    <span>80% Completo</span>
		  </div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;progress&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;progress-bar&quot; role=&quot;progressbar&quot; aria-valuenow=&quot;80&quot; aria-valuemin=&quot;0&quot; aria-valuemax=&quot;100&quot; style=&quot;width: 80%;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;60% Complete&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>


<table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
	<thead>
		<th>Atributo</th>
		<th>Descrição</th>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>aria-valuenow</td>
			<td>É onde você pode guardar o valor atual do progresso.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>arial-valuemin</td>
			<td>Qual é o valor mínimo com o qual a barra vai funcionar.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>aria-valuemax</td>
			<td>Qual valor máximo de progresso a barra chegará.</td>
		</tr>
